Perfect for various uses like reminders, messages, task organization, and more. Also used for school, office, and family. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fun Colors! Not Much Stick.
reviews.reviewText: Whoever invented sticky notes surely came up with a winner! Why do we love them so? There is something so satisfying about a new stack of colorful sticky notes, as if just owning them makes us more organized and productive.I love using sticky notes when I scrapbook. I might look at a few photos of a grandson playing soccer, and think that it might be great to get some soccer stickers the next time I'm out shopping. So I'll use two sticky notes. I put one on the photo, explaining why I didn't finish scrapbooking that photo - because I want to add soccer stickers - and then I write another sticky note to put in my purse, reminding me to buy soccer stickers.We use sticky notes to communicate with the grandkids' teachers. If I just write on a slip of paper, it's likely to get lost before the teacher can see it. But a sticky note in a bright color is sure to catch the teacher's attention.There is less adhesive on these sticky notes than there is on the name-brand product. If you mostly stick things to paper, that won't be a problem. If you stick them to a wall, they probably won't stay there.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent quality and vibrant colors
reviews.reviewText: I have to start this review by admitting that I'm somewhat addicted to sticky notes. I find it hard to resist buying them, and I have a variety of sizes and colors, both plain and printed with cute sayings and graphics. This set of eight sticky pads was a terrific addition to my collection! At just under a dollar a pad, they're an excellent value, quite a bit less expensive than purchasing at an office supply store. Assuming, of course, you could find colorful ones like this at the office supply store. They are quite sticky, I find them comparable in stickiness to the popular name brand. You know which one I mean! I've had several of them stuck on the cork board next to my desk for days now, and they don't show any signs of going anywhere. They also don't leave any marks when removed from most surfaces I've tried them on. All these things combined result in an excellent quality product. Highly recommended!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars nice amount of papers, but not super sticky
reviews.reviewText: I got these for my daughter, who likes to leave little notes for people and use them for her homework. She loves the different colors and the many papers this set comes with. However, she said that these are not so sticky as compared to other sticky notes brands she has gotten (Post-It). These will last her for a while and they will do, but just aren't as sticky.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is a package of a mixture of eight brightly colored and pastel sticky notes. Each sticky note measures 3x3 in. There are 80 sheets in each sticky note pad for a total of 640 sticky notes in all. They seem to stick well I have had one hanging on the edge of the table beside me for several days now and it has stayed in place with its sticky back. These can be used in school or in an office setting or just used around the house to place notes wherever you need them placed.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Not sticky enough
reviews.reviewText: They are really pretty colors. I found that the sticky area is just too light. I was using them for making notes and they didn't stay stuck to my table. The adhesive may be enough to stay stuck to paper but not other hard objects. They are adequate but i prefer name brand sticky notes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Handy sticky notes just like name brand
reviews.reviewText: I ordered the sticky notes pack for my home. I remembered finding them very useful at work and thought that they might prove so around the house as well. The sticky notes themselves seem to be comparable to name brand sticky notes that I have used in the past. They offer good adhesion and come in a pleasing array of different bright colors. I am sure that I will get a lot of use out of them in the future.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality sticky notes
reviews.reviewText: These sticky notes are just as good as the ones from the national brand I will not mention by name, but you know who I am talking about. The "sticky" is not too sticky or too little sticky, but just right. There are multiple colors, so if you need to color code your notes or items you have eight to choose from. At just under $1 per 80 sheet pad of sticky notes, these are a great value!
